Cloudfare DNS service(1.1.1.1) it will improve ur browsing speed by 25% and it is specially setup to prevent ur privacy and
prevent ur ISP from tracking ur browsing activities, most of the times DNS is selected by routers IP which can tell all ur
History.

Change DNS on Kali Linux ->
cmd -> vim /etc/resolv.conf and change the nameserver as 1.1.1.1

check on the 'standard test' on dnsleaktest.com the ISP should be now Cloudflare



